---
import SiteLayout from '../layouts/SiteLayout.astro';
import Icon from '../components/Icon.astro';
import { colorTokens, designSource, radiusTokens, spacingTokens, typeTokens } from '../data/system';
---
<SiteLayout title="Lab — Design / index" description="The live local specimen surface for Design Contract tokens, components, and layouts." active="lab">
  <section class="lab-hero page-frame"><div><p class="eyebrow"><span class="eyebrow-rule"></span> Official test surface</p><h1>See the contract<br /><em>working.</em></h1><p>The Lab renders the system as a working interface. It is where tokens become geometry, components become behavior, and rules become something you can inspect in a browser.</p></div><div class="lab-index-card"><span>REFERENCE BUILD</span><strong>v1.1</strong><div><i></i><i></i><i></i><i></i><i></i></div><small>static / local / inspectable</small></div></section>
  <nav class="lab-rail page-frame" aria-label="Lab sections"><a href="#foundations">Foundations</a><a href="#components">Components</a><a href="#layout">Layout</a><a href="#data">Data display</a><a href="/evaluate/">Evaluation <Icon name="arrow" size={14} /></a></nav>
  <section id="foundations" class="lab-section page-frame"><div class="lab-section-heading"><div><p class="eyebrow"><span class="eyebrow-rule"></span> Foundations</p><h2>Tokens with a job.</h2></div><p>Every value earns its place by carrying hierarchy, rhythm, or state. The specimen is read directly from <code>{designSource}</code>.</p></div><div class="lab-panel color-panel"><div class="panel-label"><span>COLOR / SEMANTIC ROLES / {designSource}</span><span>{colorTokens.length} shown</span></div><div class="swatch-grid">{colorTokens.map((token) => <div class="swatch"><span class="swatch-color" style={`background:${token.value}`}></span><div><strong>{token.name}</strong><small>{token.role}</small><code>{token.value}</code></div></div>)}</div></div><div class="foundation-split"><div class="lab-panel type-panel"><div class="panel-label"><span>TYPE / SCALE / {designSource}</span><span>{typeTokens.length} roles</span></div><div class="type-list">{typeTokens.map((token) => <div class="type-row"><span>{token.name}</span><strong style={`font-size:${token.size};font-weight:${token.weight};line-height:${token.leading}`}>{token.sample}</strong><code>{token.size} / {token.leading}</code></div>)}</div></div><div class="lab-panel token-panel"><div class="panel-label"><span>SPACE / RHYTHM / {designSource}</span><span>4px fine grid</span></div><div class="space-list">{spacingTokens.map((token) => <div class="space-row"><span>{token.name}</span><i style={`width:${token.value}`}></i><code>{token.value}</code><small>{token.use}</small></div>)}</div><div class="radius-list">{radiusTokens.map((token) => <div><span style={`border-radius:${token.value}`}></span><code>{token.name}</code></div>)}</div></div></div></section>
  <section id="components" class="lab-section lab-section-border page-frame"><div class="lab-section-heading"><div><p class="eyebrow"><span class="eyebrow-rule"></span> Components</p><h2>Intent before ornament.</h2></div><p>These are deliberately small specimens: enough to verify role, state, and ownership without pretending to be a component library.</p></div><div class="component-specimens"><div class="lab-panel specimen-panel"><div class="panel-label"><span>ACTIONS / COMMITMENT</span><span>one primary / region</span></div><div class="button-specimen"><a class="button button-primary" href="#components">Primary action <Icon name="arrow" size={15} /></a><a class="button button-secondary" href="#components">Secondary action</a><a class="specimen-text-link" href="#components">Tertiary link <Icon name="arrow" size={14} /></a></div><div class="state-line"><span class="status status-core">Ready</span><span class="status status-normative">Normative</span><span class="status status-reference">Reference</span></div></div><div class="lab-panel specimen-panel"><div class="panel-label"><span>NAVIGATION / PEERS</span><span>local representation</span></div><nav class="tabs-specimen" aria-label="Specimen navigation"><a class="tab-active" aria-current="page" href="#components">Overview</a><a href="#components">Tokens</a><a href="#components">Evidence</a></nav><div class="notice-specimen"><span class="note-dot"></span><p>Current location remains visible without relying on hover.</p></div></div></div></section>
  <section id="layout" class="lab-section page-frame"><div class="lab-section-heading"><div><p class="eyebrow"><span class="eyebrow-rule"></span> Layout</p><h2>One frame, clear owners.</h2></div><p>Shell, content, and supporting pane share one geometry system. Supporting context transforms before the work collapses.</p></div><div class="layout-demo lab-panel"><div class="demo-sidebar"><span class="demo-logo"></span><span class="demo-active"></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></div><div class="demo-work"><div class="demo-toolbar"><span></span><span></span><i></i></div><div class="demo-heading"><small>COLLECTION / 01</small><strong>Make the structure visible.</strong><div></div></div><div class="demo-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></div></div><div class="demo-inspector"><small>INSPECTOR</small><span></span><span></span><span></span><i></i></div></div></section>
  <section id="data" class="lab-section lab-section-border page-frame"><div class="lab-section-heading"><div><p class="eyebrow"><span class="eyebrow-rule"></span> Data display</p><h2>Dense when comparison matters.</h2></div><p>Rows align identity, status, and the next action without turning every cell into a separate card.</p></div><div class="lab-panel table-panel"><div class="panel-label"><span>RECENT CONTRACTS</span><span>4 records / stable columns</span></div><div class="lab-table" role="table" aria-label="Recent design contracts"><div class="table-row table-head" role="row"><span>Contract</span><span>Surface</span><span>Status</span><span>Updated</span></div><div class="table-row" role="row"><strong>Warm Paper Workbench</strong><span>web app</span><span class="table-status"><i></i>Current</span><time>Today</time></div><div class="table-row" role="row"><strong>Quiet Commerce</strong><span>marketing</span><span class="table-status"><i></i>Review</span><time>Yesterday</time></div><div class="table-row" role="row"><strong>Field Notes</strong><span>mobile</span><span class="table-status is-muted"><i></i>Draft</span><time>3 days ago</time></div></div></div></section>
</SiteLayout>
